						<div class="postbody">Is this glitchy line exclusive to Super Mario Bros?  I can't think of any reason at the moment why that line should be occurring at all, since the only time anything is written to the PPU during display is after a sprite #0 hit is detected.  And that happens farther up the screen.</div>

					
