				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p112235">Re: Random glitchy line in Super Mario Bros. on real hardwar</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=112235#p112235"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu May 16, 2013 9:33 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
				</tr>
				</table>
			</td>
