						<div class="postbody">Is that a piece of pipe on that line inbetween the 3 and 2 pipes? Given that the rest of the line look like breakable block tiles, that must be from the very top-most row of blocks that you run across when going to the warp zone normally (the pipe tiles would be the ones that Mario's head goes through when doing the world 36-1 glitch).<br /><br />OT: This is strangely similar to some analysis I did on some footage of the 80's game show Press Your Luck a few years ago (that is unfortunately no longer online), when trying to track down a pattern to slides that would stick as the board would shuffle from one set of projectors to the other. That was possibly even more deterministic than this, however.</div>

